---
title: Cheesy Turkey Hash with Cheddar Cheese and Sour Cream
description: For a hearty and simple meal that packs a punch, we've got you covered! Succulent turkey is coated in Enchilada Spice Blend and paired with herbaceous green onions, a mix of roasted russet and sweet potatoes, sautéed peppers and topped off with tangy sour cream.
